00:22:24.330 --> 00:22:25.610
Gracias.

00:22:27.010 --> 00:22:29.150
Disculpe.

00:22:32.450 --> 00:22:34.120
Decker.

00:22:35.990 --> 00:22:37.650
¿Que hizo qué?

00:22:46.600 --> 00:22:48.060
